data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience in this beautifully maintained home. Boasting an inviting atmosphere, this residence is designed for relaxation and entertainment. As you step inside, you're greeted by the warm embrace of oak hardwood floors that pave the way through the home's interior. The heart of this home features a beautifully updated bathroom, showcasing modern fixtures and finishes that blend seamlessly with the home's character. Downstairs you will find a spacious family room and a legal bedroom, offering versatility and extra space for your family's needs. Location is everything, and this home does not disappoint. Situated in a friendly neighborhood, you're just moments away from shopping, dining, and entertainment options. This Bloomington gem combines the privacy of a quiet residential area with the accessibility of city living. It's not just a house; it's your next home, ready to create lasting memories.
